  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为这款3D赛车游戏设计一个云原生架构图。核心入口是Main模块，它应该部署在Serverless环境里，负责启动整个游戏。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Main",
        "CloudNative_Serverless"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，Main作为入口点。那游戏主体部分怎么安排？是用Helm Chart来管理吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Game",
        "CloudNative_HelmChart"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，Game模块用Helm Chart部署。它要驱动ThreeScene渲染引擎，这个渲染集群需要K8s来弹性伸缩。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Game",
        "ThreeScene",
        "CloudNative_K8sCluster"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把Main指向Game，然后Game通过\"Renderiza\"关系连接到ThreeScene。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Main",
        "Game",
        "ThreeScene"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "游戏还需要导入资源。Car和Track都要从外部导入，Car做成DockerImage方便版本控制，Track继续用Helm Chart管理配置。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Car",
        "Track",
        "CloudNative_DockerImage",
        "CloudNative_HelmChart"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下：Game通过\"Importa\"关系同时连接Car和Track，对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Game",
        "Car",
        "Track"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错。另外游戏运行时需要几个Hook模块：Physics物理引擎、Controls控制逻辑、Camera摄像机系统。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Physics",
        "Controls",
        "Camera"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "这三个Hook的部署方式有区别吗？Physics和Camera我打算放K8s集群，Controls用DockerImage独立部署，这样符合微服务拆分吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Physics",
        "Camera",
        "Controls",
        "CloudNative_K8sCluster",
        "CloudNative_DockerImage"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "完全正确。Controls需要快速迭代，DockerImage更灵活；Physics和Camera对计算资源要求高，K8s能自动扩缩容。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Controls",
        "Physics",
        "Camera"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加三条Hook连线，都标注为\"Hook\"。现在ThreeScene需要直接引用Car和Track资源吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ThreeScene",
        "Car",
        "Track"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，ThreeScene渲染时要直接访问Car模型和Track赛道数据。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ThreeScene",
        "Car",
        "Track"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "架构基本成型了。未来规划里是不是还要加个Hub社区功能和Editor编辑器？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Hub",
        "Editor"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，这两个是远期功能。Hub做玩家社区，用Serverless省成本；Editor是关卡编辑器，用Helm Chart部署。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Hub",
        "Editor",
        "CloudNative_Serverless",
        "CloudNative_HelmChart"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已用\"Futuro\"标注这两条未来扩展线。我检查一下整体流向：Main→Game→ThreeScene，同时Game辐射出Importa和Hook两组依赖。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Main",
        "Game",
        "ThreeScene"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 15,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，Car的部署方式我刚才说DockerImage，但Track也是赛道配置，为什么Track不用DockerImage？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Car",
        "Track"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 16,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "我注意到这个问题了。实际上Car是运行时镜像，Track是静态配置+动态参数，用Helm Chart的values文件管理多环境部署更合理。需要我把Car改成HelmChart吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Car",
        "Track"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 17,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "不用改，保持现状。Car作为可执行组件需要容器化，Track作为纯数据配置适合Helm。这个区分是有意的。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Car",
        "Track"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 18,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "标题我暂定为\"Arquitetura do Jogo de Corrida 3D\"，需要调整吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "title"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 19,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "可以，保留葡萄牙语标题，这个项目是巴西团队主导的。最后确认一下：Futuro的两条线Hub和Editor，优先级有区别吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Hub",
